OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773288217
OL,3,CVoters can judge me in 2031 if I miss
OL,4,Cchild poverty target ` Swinney
OL,6,FPressed again on whether he will quit
OL,7,Fif he misses the target, the First
OL,8,FMinister said: "People will be able to
OL,9,Fsee what I've done by 2031... it's
OL,10,Fentirely up to the public to make
OL,11,Ftheir judgment.
OL,13,F"But I'm confident that I can give the
OL,14,Fleadership and the direction and the
OL,15,Fresources and the policy interventions
OL,16,Fto make sure that we achieve those
OL,17,Ftargets."
OL,26,@pD@POUuD@AOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
