OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773288217
OL,3,CVoters can judge me in 2031 if I miss
OL,4,Cchild poverty target ` Swinney
OL,6,FThe First Minister's comments come as
OL,7,Fthe Government prepared to unveil a
OL,8,Fnew child poverty plan on Thursday,
OL,9,Fwhich will cover the next
OL,10,Fparliamentary session.
OL,12,FSpeaking ahead of the publication,
OL,13,FSocial Justice Secretary Shirley-Anne
OL,14,FSomerville said the plan will "provide
OL,15,Fa brighter future for every child".
OL,17,FShe added: "It will focus on tackling
OL,18,Fthe root causes of child poverty,
OL,19,Fboosting incomes, and reducing
OL,20,Feveryday costs.
OL,26,@vD@_OUwD@bO]yD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773288217
OL,3,CVoters can judge me in 2031 if I miss
OL,4,Cchild poverty target ` Swinney
OL,6,F"It will also include details on how
OL,7,Fwe will further embed support where
OL,8,Fpeople need it, when people need it,
OL,9,Fby ensuring the public and third
OL,10,Fsector act as one in communities
OL,11,Facross the country.
OL,13,F"Through bold action, rates of
OL,14,Frelative child poverty in Scotland
OL,15,Fhave reached the lowest in almost a
OL,16,Fdecade, standing nine percentage
OL,17,Fpoints below the UK average.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
