PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773288217
OL,3,CVoters can judge me in 2031 if I miss
OL,4,Cchild poverty target ` Swinney
OL,6,F"Policies only seen in Scotland, like
OL,7,Fthe Scottish child payment, are
OL,8,Fcentral to this, and giving more
OL,9,Fchildren the opportunity to thrive.
OL,11,F"Ensuring that is the case for every
OL,12,Fchild remains our top priority."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUtD@`O]
